ntsb3723txt-1-5-5-0-1 The pilot stated the right front seat passenger deployed the spoilers during the flare to land causing a hard landing. 
ntsb3723txt-1-5-5-0-5 The pilot did not apply power and the airplane landed then veered off the runway. 
ntsb3723txt-1-5-5-0-6 He stated 'in retrospect, he probably shouldn't have kept the spoilers out after bouncing', and he previously agreed with the pilot to keep the spoilers deployed once activated. 
ntsb3723txt-1-5-5-0-8 Only following the bounce, did he see the right front passenger activate the spoilers. 
